 One Direction is a only week away from releasing their highly-anticipated new album, "Midnight Memories". However, the British/Irish boyband's third studio effort unexpectedly surfaced online on Monday, November 18. 

The songs that leaked included the album's lead single "Best Song Ever", current single "Story of My Life" as well as the title track, "Midnight Memories". For fans who can't wait until next week, the album's early arrival is exciting.
